{"tid":1691184,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！11月4日早上9點報名《禁蒙面法》公聽會","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T08:58:56.000Z","uid":294109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70b70e3c3c7a0620338b64d33cb08637ffbdfde8","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X08q3XH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX08q3XH.png&h=a6b74a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【公聽會要人！】#和理非戰線<br />\n召集所有受《蒙面法》影響嘅市民出嚟發聲！蒙面警隨街恐嚇、濫捕濫告戴口罩嘅香港人，令到市民病都唔敢帶口罩出街、醫護人員戴口罩被捕、記者係催淚彈爆發嘅時候俾警察強行除口罩、國際社會對香港更加失去信心等等⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n政府早前繞過正常立法程序，強行用緊急法訂立蒙面惡法，而家又打算靠保皇黨護航下「以先訂立後審議」方式極速取得立法會授權，所以戰線時間有限，公聽會發言機會好重要！而由於小組委員會罕有限定公聽會名額得150個，相信保皇黨係打算派人搶佔盡量多嘅發言機會，製造好多人支持《蒙面法》嘅輿論。<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，我哋唔可以比佢哋得逞，所以和理非們，輪到你地嘅回合，輪到你哋上戰場保護其他香港人，輸到你地俾子彈國際傳媒報導香港真相！<br />\n<br />\n懇請大家嚟緊今個星期一（4/11）上晝9點，準時一齊上網報名嚟公聽會，我地好需要真正嘅民意進入立法會！#我有權 #戴口罩！<br />\n<br />\n立法會《禁止蒙面規例》<br />\n小組委員會公聽會<br />\n報名日期：11月4日 9:00am<br />\n會議日期：11月9日 9:00am - 6:00pm<br />\n報名網址：<a href=\"https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.legco.gov.hk%2Fors%2Fchinese%2FList.aspx&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=77042f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"fd25384c699c3f1e644a31dba221ac0ede39d394","tid":1691184,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ed82692c2c6d663ba79a6fd6d322a648be6bd17","tid":1691184,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:28:16.000Z","msg":"曱甴近平"},{"pid":"c80d0da93727605d959f3dbf36927f7c3b153977","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:31:25.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁，大家幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94cc0df185b5ee9763a1d2a127c7a93fd02b778","tid":1691184,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:34:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6060c3c0a546314cf3d05e5cb4d128b8ae56f19","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"多一個手足入到場就多一把聲音"},{"pid":"f6c7579e96553cd7686d9c3e29b7ed20c1e3b5bb","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"好想做到林奠見面會個次大比數民意反對《禁蒙面法》"},{"pid":"44304786db2e49aab4ed65d458c8cff192ecf6d8","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"推行動post，得150個位！"},{"pid":"3275fdb799017a30b63fd3bfd5bbf07b458b4057","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"繼續推！"},{"pid":"ae619b69f4eb162c7f7656ecfc99d4a07f52b35e","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"推上熱門！"},{"pid":"c2937f1da713f9563ded55d9dcbde129da8db7a1","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bd0d3ed1691fd2c3a9ee2ba6a1dfe42b9f0e18ab","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"3427fa9ab0d35ca5d981adbb6f765c0ad4c99483","tid":1691184,"uid":262115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:06:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98b8b58f33cd7f2bccd7757fffa21cc54b315f7d","tid":1691184,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:17:24.000Z","msg":"推呀屌"},{"pid":"8ed2c084c935fd7a958394f401106ecf139ba643","tid":1691184,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:42:40.000Z","msg":"意見書有冇咩格式要跟?<br />\n冇既就自由發揮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf85a594742d55856963435973cc895b76a4ae45","tid":1691184,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70b70e3c3c7a0620338b64d33cb08637ffbdfde8","tid":1691184,"uid":294109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X08q3XH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX08q3XH.png&h=a6b74a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【公聽會要人！】#和理非戰線<br />\n召集所有受《蒙面法》影響嘅市民出嚟發聲！蒙面警隨街恐嚇、濫捕濫告戴口罩嘅香港人，令到市民病都唔敢帶口罩出街、醫護人員戴口罩被捕、記者係催淚彈爆發嘅時候俾警察強行除口罩、國際社會對香港更加失去信心等等⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n政府早前繞過正常立法程序，強行用緊急法訂立蒙面惡法，而家又打算靠保皇黨護航下「以先訂立後審議」方式極速取得立法會授權，所以戰線時間有限，公聽會發言機會好重要！而由於小組委員會罕有限定公聽會名額得150個，相信保皇黨係打算派人搶佔盡量多嘅發言機會，製造好多人支持《蒙面法》嘅輿論。<br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，我哋唔可以比佢哋得逞，所以和理非們，輪到你地嘅回合，輪到你哋上戰場保護其他香港人，輸到你地俾子彈國際傳媒報導香港真相！<br />\n<br />\n懇請大家嚟緊今個星期一（4/11）上晝9點，準時一齊上網報名嚟公聽會，我地好需要真正嘅民意進入立法會！#我有權 #戴口罩！<br />\n<br />\n立法會《禁止蒙面規例》<br />\n小組委員會公聽會<br />\n報名日期：11月4日 9:00am<br />\n會議日期：11月9日 9:00am - 6:00pm<br />\n報名網址：<a href=\"https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.legco.gov.hk%2Fors%2Fchinese%2FList.aspx&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=77042f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"本人反對禁止蒙面法。原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n第一，此法違反《基本法》27條：「香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由」。政府將《禁蒙面法》適用於合法遊行集會，令人質疑此舉的真正目的是阻嚇一般市民和學生不要上街抗議，否則承擔被秋後算帳的後果。𣎴少市民害怕在集會露面會影響其工作或私隱，例如公司的政治立場與員工不符，員工擔心參加合法集會會被公司䜔責；同志遊行的參與者希望爭取平權，但礙於社會歧視和壓力，暫時未能露面表態等。因此，此法嚴重損害市民無畏無懼地行使言論自由的權利。<br />\n<br />\n第二，此法對警員及香港市民雙重標準。<br />\n《禁蒙面法》生效後，一方面是警員依然遮蓋其委任證，甚至戴黑口罩雙重隱瞞身份。另一方面，普通市民連戴衛生口罩出外也隨時被警員截停查問。例如，不少記者被警員扯下其防催淚彈的面罩。（註一）有患癌症的市民展示其醫生紙卻被警員視為偽造文件等。（註二）法例通過後的穩定社會成效未見，但市民對政府和警方的不滿卻再創新高！<br />\n<br />\n因此，禁蒙面法只會增加民憤，完全無法做到預期的止暴制亂的效果。希望政府能順應民意，取消惡法。 <br />\n<br />\n第三，香港空氣污染指數愈來愈嚴重，全因警察胡亂放催淚彈，促使有需要使用衛生口罩！保護其個人身體健康 <br />\n<br />\n香港市民  XXX上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註一：-記者遭警強扯面罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F391108%2F%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%BC%B7%E6%89%AF%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%89-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%84%A1%E7%89%B9%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=c560cba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/391108/禁蒙面法-記者遭警強扯面罩-黃定光-記者無特權違反警方指示</a><br />\n<br />\n註二：癌漢戴口罩 警屈偽造醫生紙<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=7804765c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FGHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI%2F&h=1c50dcfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/GHUMTYKXLOJXF6YRET3ZKZN4RI/</a>"}]}